-- Health Care REIT to buy HealthLease for $950 mln
-- By Anand Basu in Bangalore
-- Wed Aug 13, 2014 08:06AM EDT
-- None



Aug 13 (Reuters) - Health Care REIT Inc <HCN.N> said it had agreed to acquire Canada's HealthLease Properties Real Estate Investment Trust <HLP_u.TO> in a deal valued at $950 million.

Health Care REIT will pay C$14.20 ($13) in cash for each HealthLease share, which represents a premium of 31 percent to HealthLease's Monday closing. [ID:nBw8L8sM7a]